        <item>
            <title>WhatsApp 新四大编辑讯息功能　可选择文字直接编辑</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/whatsapp-20/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=whatsapp-20</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/whatsapp-20/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:30:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[WhatsApp]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221145</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">WhatsApp 更新推出四项新编辑文字讯息格式功能，可助用家整理文字，及提升用文字信息沟通的效率。现已适用于 Android、iOS、Web 及 Mac 桌面用家。用家需要将 WhatsApp 更新至最新版本 ，即可使用四大新编辑文字讯息格式功能。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221151 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3225-631x580.jpg" alt="" width="631" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3225-631x580.jpg 631w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3225.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 631px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221146 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3227-621x580.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3227-621x580.jpg 621w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3227.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 621px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iOS 用家可将 WhatsApp 更新至 24.4.3 版本</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>项目符号清单</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">用家只要输入「-」及在后面输入空格，即可获得如食谱的格式，方便阅读。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221147 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3221-689x580.jpg" alt="" width="689" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3221-689x580.jpg 689w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3221.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 689px" /></p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>编号清单</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">有时想顺序列出细项，过往就必须手动打上数字并分次序，现时只要在第一个项目上输入「1.」并在后面多输入一个空格，用家按下一行时，就会自动出现「2.」，不再手动输入数字，条理更清晰。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221148 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3222-682x580.jpg" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3222-682x580.jpg 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3222.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/12/whatsapp-in-app-sticker-edit/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】WhatsApp 内自制贴图，可在旧贴图上画公仔</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/14/whatsapp-to-sync-chat-locks-across-devices-for-enhanced-security/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 测试跨设备聊天锁，提升讯息保安能力</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/10/whatsapp-interoperability-messaging/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 准备加入跨平台互通支援　欧盟规定需要容许平台互通</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>引号</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">用家可输入「&gt;」及一个空格，即可得到引号，方便用家引用其他文字。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221149 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3223-694x530.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="530" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3223-694x530.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3223.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>行内代码</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">此功能有助用家在分辨句子中的特别讯息，在输入文字时可加上反引号「`」就可以了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221150 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3224-694x529.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="529" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3224-694x529.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3224.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">而旧有的功能，如粗体、斜体、删除线及等宽字体选项，只要选择文字就可直接编辑。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221152 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3226-665x580.jpg" alt="" width="665" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3226-665x580.jpg 665w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3226.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 665px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/12/whatsapp-in-app-sticker-edit/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】WhatsApp 内自制贴图，可在旧贴图上画公仔</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/14/whatsapp-to-sync-chat-locks-across-devices-for-enhanced-security/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 测试跨设备聊天锁，提升讯息保安能力</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/10/whatsapp-interoperability-messaging/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 准备加入跨平台互通支援　欧盟规定需要容许平台互通</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/whatsapp-20/software/">WhatsApp 新四大编辑讯息功能　可选择文字直接编辑</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
