        </item>
        <item>
            <title>《Contra: Operation Galuga》初代魂斗罗重制版【有片睇】多平台推出试玩版</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/contra-operation-galuga-launches-march-12-demo-now-available/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=contra-operation-galuga-launches-march-12-demo-now-available</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/contra-operation-galuga-launches-march-12-demo-now-available/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:00:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[《Contra: Operation Galuga》]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[魂斗罗]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221072</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>发行商 Konami 与开发商 WayForward 联合宣布，经典卷轴类射击游戏《魂斗罗》将于 3 月 12 日于 Steam、PlayStation 5、PlayStation 4、Xbox Series、Xbox One 及 Switch 推出初代重制版《Contra: Operation Galuga》。实体版本于 3 月 1 日起可透过 Limited Run Games 预购。现时全部平台均已有试玩版让玩家热身，等待正式版推出。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221114" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221115" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《Contra: Operation Galuga》是 80 年代经典卷轴射击游戏《魂斗罗》的重制版，除了提升画质、音效等，这次重制版亦加入了新的关卡、敌人、头目、武器等。故事模式下最高支援 2 个玩家；街机模式则最高支援 4 个玩家。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-7-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-7-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-7.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲故事模式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221116" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-2-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-2-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221117" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-3-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-3-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-3.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221118" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-4-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-4-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-4.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-5-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-5-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-5.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲是次加入了不少新的技能和武器</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-6-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-6-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-6.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_63156"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mIoyoDgBn9o?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mIoyoDgBn9o">Konami@YouTube</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/02/contra-operation-galuga-launches-march-12-demo-now-available">Gematsu</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/contra-operation-galuga-launches-march-12-demo-now-available/game-channel/">《Contra: Operation Galuga》初代魂斗罗重制版【有片睇】多平台推出试玩版</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
