        <item>
            <title>《GUNDAM Breaker4》今年登场，特典版情报全公开</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/gundam-breaker-4/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gundam-breaker-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/gundam-breaker-4/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gundam]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GUNDAM 创坏者 4]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221041</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>备受高达迷赞赏的以高达模型为主题的《GUNDAM Breaker》系列游戏，将在今年推出第四集《GUNDAM Breaker 4》。是次会在 Nintendo Switch、PlayStation 5、PlayStation 4 及 STEAM 上登场。今日 BANDAI NAMCO 就同步公开各版本情报及首条宣传影片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221048" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/01-21-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/01-21-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/01-21.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221049" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/02-22-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/02-22-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/02-22.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>本作是动作游戏《GUNDAM Breaker》系列之最新作，玩家可以在游戏里建造专属于自己的「独门高达模型」，并以其进行战斗。玩家在任务中打倒敌人获得零件后，即可用来改装自己的独门高达模型。</p><p>在全新的「场景模型模式」中设定背景及特效等，制作专属于自己的场景。<br />
尽情展现自己的独门高达模型——</p><p>特点 1 「开创」：组合来自超过 250 架以上的机体零件，尽情改装创造独门高达模型。<br />
特点 2「战斗」：以独门高达模型挑战任务，打倒敌人即可获得零件。<br />
特点 3 「展现」：设定背景、高达模型、特效等，建立专属场景，并在完成后，拍摄精心设计的照片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221055" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/08-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/08-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/08.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>3 项全新进化</h2><p>①改装进化：左右手可改装为不同的零件或武器</p><p>在本作中，左右手可以分别设定为不同的零件，玩家将可以制作独创性远超过前作的独门高达模型。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221050" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/03-23-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/03-23-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/03-23.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221051" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/04-23-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/04-23-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/04-23.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>②动作进化：左右不同武装为动作带来大幅进化</p><p>使用装备于右手及左手的武器与技能，打造专属的连段攻击。</p><p>玩家将可以配合眼前的情况分别使用右手及左手的武器，并透过技能组合，找到自己独特的连段攻击。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221052" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/05-17-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/05-17-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/05-17.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221053" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/06-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/06-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/06-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>③游戏重点：利用全新的「场景模型模式」建造专属场景</p><p>组合独门高达模型、背景及各式各样的物件，玩家将可打造属于自己的场景。</p><p>更可于线上向其他玩家展示，获得「Good Build」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221054" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/07-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/07-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/07.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/smpvoltesv/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】SMP《V 型电磁侠》　几乎完全变形合体 + 另类关节设计高可动</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/14/gundam-seed-freedom/movie-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《高达 SEED FREEDOM》日本票房超 26.8 亿日元，高达剧场版票房最高 + YouTube 音乐祭直播庆祝</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2></h2><h2>特典、版本情报公开</h2><p><strong>实体版首批／数码版预购共通特典</strong></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221056" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/09-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/09-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/09.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>首批购买实体版或预购数码版的玩家，将可提前使用「高达（再循环配色）」完整零件组及制作人零件 6 种。</p><p><strong>Nintendo Switch／PlayStation5 版实体限定版</strong></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221057" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-co